name: Fishing Rod
description: Cast your rod into the sea for a chance to get some rewards!

name: Jay's Golden Coin
description: It's a golden coin! At one point this used to be called a Dollarydoo. It radiates a warmth that invigorates you.

name: Gates Puzzle Piece
description: In another universe this item went by another name and held a great magical power. It quietly vibrates at times.

name: Mysterious Wand
description: The wood of the wand is oak and smells of lavender and burnt linens. You feel a great power inside.
